sections.heading: Memorial Fund; Board of Regents; duties
sections.text: The Board of Regents of the University of Nebraska shall carry into effect the purposes of sections 85-167 to 85-171.SourceLaws 1917, c. 239, § 2, p. 577;C.S.1922, § 6780;C.S.1929, § 85-170;R.S.1943, § 85-167;Laws 2000, LB 1135, § 29.
